  "description": "<p><u>Positions Available:</u></p><p></p><p><strong>1. Email Agent - 6 months</strong></p><p><em>Working Hours:</em></p><p>Monday to Friday: 830am - 6pm / 830am - 530pm</p><p>Alt Saturday: 830am - 1pm</p><p></p><p><strong>2. Call Centre - 1 year contract</strong></p><p><em>Working Hours:</em></p><p>Any 5 days of the week ( 4 weekdays + 1 weekend)</p><p>830am - 6pm / 11am - 9pm (rotate bi-weekly)</p><p><em>Salary: $2600</em></p><p></p><p><strong>3. Part-time Call Centre - 6 months contract</strong></p><p><em>Working Hours: </em></p><p>Monday - Friday: 10am - 2pm / 11 am - 3pm (hours may extend based on surge)</p><p><em>Salary: $13/hr</em></p><p></p><p><strong>4. Greenwich Call Centre - 1 year contract</strong><br /><br /><em>Working hours:</em></p><p>Any 5 days of the week ( 4 weekdays + 1 weekend)</p><p>7am - 445pm / 10am - 745pm</p><p>215pm - 12am (rarely)</p><p><em>Salary: $2600</em></p><p></p><p><strong>5. 3 shift Call Centre - 1 year contract</strong></p><p><em>Working Hours:</em></p><p>Any 5 days of the week including weekends and PH</p><p>a. 8am - 530pm</p><p>b. 830am - 6pm</p><p>c. 230pm - 12am</p><p>d. 1130pm - 9am</p><p><em>Salary: $2800</em></p><p></p><p><strong>6. Office hours Call Centre - 1 year contract</strong></p><p><em>Working Hours:</em></p><p>Monday to Friday: 8am - 545pm</p><p><em>Salary: $2600</em></p><p></p><p><strong>7. Project based Call Centre - 1 year contract</strong></p><p><em>Working Hours:</em></p><p>Monday to Friday: 830am - 530pm / 830am - 6pm</p><p>Alt Sat: 830am - 1pm</p><p><em>Salary: $2600</em><br /></p><p>Interested applicants, please email your updated CV to rachel.lim@recruitexpress.com.sg or WA 97527630 for more information.</p><p></p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p></p><p>EA Personnel No: R23116144</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Lim Ruo Yi, Rachel</p><p>Company EA license No.: Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599)<br /></p>",
